There will be the following classes:
- Auction
	- Parameters
		- ID
		- Minimum bid (> or = $1)
		- Buyout price
		- Time limit (4, 12, or 24 hours)
		- Time uploaded
		- Details
		- Posted (int of 0 or 1; 0 means not posted, 1 means posted)
		- HeldFunds
		- WalletHoldingFunds
		- BlockTime
	- Methods
		- UpdateUser(UserWallet) --> send message to user, updating them of auction status
		- UpdateItemStatus (TimeLimit, TimeUploaded) --> delete auction if expired
- QuickBid
	- Parameters
		- AuctionID
		- BuyerWalletAddress
		- SellerWalletAddress
		- Tax
		- CryptoPrice
	- Methods
		- Bid(Auction ID, Wallet) --> begin transaction for user
		- BuyOut(AuctionID, Wallet) --> begin and complete transaction for user
- User
	- Parameters
		- Wallet
		- PersonalIdentifier (phone number/email)
	- Methods
		- SendMessage(Message) --> send message to user's identification
		- PostAuction(AuctionNumber) --> posts an auction for the user
- UserSearch
	- Parameters
		- UserSearch
		- Filter
	- Methods
		- Search(UserSearch, Filter) --> sorts the auctions